{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"希腊孩子去美国","authors":["天马","江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":1,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"希腊孩子去美国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗  江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载：美国的人贩子集团，最近三年来，把成千上万的希腊幼儿贩运到美国。这些儿童就像邮包似的成堆成堆地被寄走了……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘生你，爹养你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生你养你不容易。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爱你，娘爱你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌上明珠心里喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里喜，只须臾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活活生生就别离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国狗强盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前来“攀亲戚”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖却心头肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运到美国去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欧洲和美洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相隔多少里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹娘念亲儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪把面洗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿把爹娘望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终日哭啼啼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住在人篱下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪像在家里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别人是主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿是小奴隶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗吃珍美味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿啃面包皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗穿绸和缎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿着破烂衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗住小楼房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿睡地窖里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗呀有人亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿呀没人理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打骂随他意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折磨无尽期！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹娘在远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望海空叹息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盗强呀强盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“攀”的好“亲戚”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是赤练蛇？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛇毒怎能比！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是黑心狼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼狠不及你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是大瘟疫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒气传千里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘟神呀瘟神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人诅咒你！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}